{
  "stem": "6944.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "My mother, Maita, she became Maria.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My father became Simon, which is a very popular-- Simone-- in France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "My brother Levi became Leon, very popular name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There is a province called Leon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And Chaim, very easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There must have been lots of Jews by the name of Chaim who converted and gave it to their children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They are called Jaime, but it's spelled with a J, because a J is a 'hu' in Spain, and they pronounced a 'hu' like the Jews, Jaime.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So we were all-- and I was Santa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Very easy, it's a Spanish name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Why my father gave me the name Santa is still a mystery to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Anyhow, the thing is that-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] --they are there, and my mother was very much liked, but she worked worked hard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "She worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And there was no [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There were at lagerheads, my father, my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Because my father just gave in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He did nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He just sat there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "He was still young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "He could have done something-- dig the garden, do something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And that aggravated my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "He was a man full of enthusiasm in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And he had nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And she wanted him to do something for his own sake.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "He refused.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So there was no [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And then when I arrived a year later, and I saw my mother do this, coming home in the evening, exhausted, I was devastated.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do, and I couldn't help her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I said, I come along with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And she says, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "No, that's not for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I became ill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "I became very ill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And they diagnosed liver illness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Well, I didn't understand it was-- and it was the stomach.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "But it took a long time for me to rehabilitate myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
